<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Paucham leh pakna phat a nuom,
 I kikhawp khawm u hin;
 I kipahna lau a chieh to,
 Ginna tha a lengin.
 Tieng chuleh kichien zawn zai tiu,
 Lungsietna thutiem chuh;
 Lei ah guolte khen mahleu hing,
 Van ah kituok hitiu.

[V2]
 Dan leh van ah kituok hitiu,
 Van ah kituok hitiu
 Isu thisan lul gin vangin,
 Van ah kituok hitiu.

[V3]
 2. Hehpihna gui kipak a um,
 I lunguh kankhawm chuh;
 Krista, Pathien Cha min deih um,
 A I kikhawp tieng leh!
 Kikhenna hung um mahlele,
 Bible in ei hilh hi;
 Kinepna deih um dantak leh,
 Van ah kituok hitiu.

[V4]
 3. Lei ah chawlin chau mahleu hing,
 Luigal tung pai tai tiu;
 I ngaihteu in ei ngaknau mun,
 Chunglam a gamnuom ah.
 Buoina huihpi I thuok u hi,
 Phat chawmcha sung hinna;
 La sa'n kumsawt kipahna tawh,
 Vanah kituok hitiu.</lyrics>
<title>HOW SWEET THE HOUR</title>
<hymn_number>338</hymn_number>
</song>